(983, 143, 'Kitchen Area wherein we check to ensure its cleanliness, garbage bin, sink, drainage & grease trap.', 'Read the questions carefully and encircle the correct answer.', 'MCQ', 1, 'Bar sink', 'Dishwashing area', 'Roasting area', 'Stockroom', 'Dishwashing area'),
