(1110, 148, 'Which goal is written in a S.M.A.R.T. way?', 'Choose the correct answer.', 'MCQ', 1, 'Always provide excellent customer service', 'Train staff to serve customers better by end of quarter', 'Increase customer satisfaction scores by 30% within three months by conducting weekly service coaching and monitoring customer feedback', 'Improve service quality regularly', 'Increase customer satisfaction scores by 30% within three months by conducting weekly service coaching and monitoring customer feedback'),
(1111, 148, 'Which of the following goals is written in a S.M.A.R.T. way?', 'Choose the correct answer.', 'MCQ', 1, 'Improve teamwork and customer service as soon as possible.', 'Increase delivery sales by 35% within three months by distributing 5,000 flyers within the delivery area.', 'Encourage employees to work better and avoid mistakes by end of quarter.', 'Make sure everyone does their best at work.', 'Increase delivery sales by 35% within three months by distributing 5,000 flyers within the delivery area.');
